<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAMLCwgAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://static.cambridge.org/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline2.png?pub-status=live" class="aop-lazy-load-image mathjax-alternative mathjax-alt-graphic mathjax-off" width="6" height="11" data-original-image="/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline2.png" data-zoomable="false">
<span class="mathjax-tex-wrapper" data-mathjax-type="texmath"><span class="tex-math mathjax-tex-math mathjax-on">$ {}_3 $</span></span></span>
</span> refer to the direct effect of each structural factor, while Hypothesis <em class="italic">HDA</em>
<span data-mathjax-status="alt-graphic" class="inline-formula">
<span class="alternatives">
<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAMLCwgAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://static.cambridge.org/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline3.png?pub-status=live" class="aop-lazy-load-image mathjax-alternative mathjax-alt-graphic mathjax-off" width="7" height="10" data-original-image="/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline3.png" data-zoomable="false">
<span class="mathjax-tex-wrapper" data-mathjax-type="texmath"><span class="tex-math mathjax-tex-math mathjax-on">$ {}_4 $</span></span></span>
</span> presents their joint effect on the demand for criminal aid: </p><ul class="list nomark">
<li class="list-item">

<p class="p"><span class="label">•</span> 
<em class="italic">HDA</em>
<span data-mathjax-status="alt-graphic" class="inline-formula">
<span class="alternatives">
<img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAMLCwgAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://static.cambridge.org/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline4.png?pub-status=live" class="aop-lazy-load-image mathjax-alternative mathjax-alt-graphic mathjax-off" width="6" height="11" data-original-image="/binary/version/id/urn:cambridge.org:id:binary:20251018043725675-0848:S0003055425101251:S0003055425101251_inline4.png" data-zoomable="false">
<span class="mathjax-tex-wrapper" data-mathjax-type="texmath"><span class="tex-math mathjax-tex-math mathjax-on">$ {}_1 $</span></span></span>
</span>: Severe economic difficulties increase demand for criminal aid.</p>
</li>
<li class="list-item">

<p class="p"><span class="label">•</span> 
