      </div> <div class="circle-list__item__grouped"><div id="reference-9-content" class="circle-list__item__grouped__content"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Astorga</span>, <span class="given-names">Luis</span></span>. <span class="year">2005</span>. <span class="source">El Siglo de Las Drogas: El Narcotráfico, del Porfiriato al Nuevo Milenio</span>. <span class="publisher-loc">Mexico City, Mexico</span>: <span class="publisher-name">Plaza y Janés</span>.<a class='ref-link' target='_blank' aria-label='Google Scholar link for El Siglo de Las Drogas: El Narcotráfico, del Porfiriato al Nuevo Milenio' href=https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=El+Siglo+de+Las+Drogas%3A+El+Narcotr%C3%A1fico%2C+del+Porfiriato+al+Nuevo+Milenio&author=Astorga+Luis&publication+year=2005>Google Scholar</a></div></div></div><div id="r9" aria-flowto="reference-10-content reference-10-button" class="circle-list__item"><!----> <div class="circle-list__item__indicator"><AppButton icon="up-circle" aria-label="Return to the reference 10 in the content" id="reference-10-button" class="circle-list__item__indicator__up"></AppButton></div> <div aria-hidden="true" data-test-hidden="true" class="circle-list__item__number">
        
      </div> <div class="circle-list__item__grouped"><div id="reference-10-content" class="circle-list__item__grouped__content"><span class="string-name"><span class="surname">Avelar</span>, <span class="given-names">Bryan</span></span>. <span class="year">2020</span>. “Un Reparto de víveres Bajo el Control de la MS-13.” <em class="italic">Revista Factum</em>.<a class='ref-link' target='_blank' aria-label='Google Scholar link for Avelar, Bryan. 2020. “Un Reparto de víveres Bajo el Control de la MS-13.” Revista Factum.' href=https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Avelar,+Bryan.+2020.+“Un+Reparto+de+víveres+Bajo+el+Control+de+la+MS-13.”+Revista+Factum.>Google Scholar</a></div></div></div><div id="r10" aria-flowto="reference-11-content reference-11-button" class="circle-list__item"><!----> <div class="circle-list__item__indicator"><AppButton icon="up-circle" aria-label="Return to the reference 11 in the content" id="reference-11-button" class="circle-list__item__indicator__up"></AppButton></div> <div aria-hidden="true" data-test-hidden="true" class="circle-list__item__number">
        
